message: The Brainerd Lakes Area Sex Trafficking Team meets monthly and had a short panel discussion Jan. 25—part of National Slavery and Human Trafficking Prevention month.

data.description: People may not have heard about any sex stings in the Brainerd lakes area for some time—but that doesn't mean the issue has disappeared.It just means traffickers have to figure out a different way of advertising to solicit customers, after a new law went into effect last year making websites accou...
